Additionally, I&#39;m using a _-1_ as the second argument of the _[String#split](https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/20/docs/api/java.base/java/lang/String.html#split(java.lang.String,int))_ call.  This will preserve trailing commas, in the event any of the data in the file is empty.

