## EDIT

Please note that the above example can be improved. You will need to know more about how CORS works. Please see [here][cors-mdn-docs]. For one, you will get the headers for all responses. This may not be desirable. You may just need to handle the preflight (or OPTIONS). If you want to see a better implemented CORS filter, you can check out the source code for the [RESTeasy `CorsFilter`][resteasy-cors-filter]

