    1997 Titanic
    1999 The Matrix
    2014 Interstellar
    2014 The Hobbit: The Battle of the Five Armies

It&#39;s probably worth noting that insertion sorts are relatively inefficient for anything oher than small lists.

  [1]: https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/lang/Comparable.html
  [2]: https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/lang/String.html#compareTo-java.lang.String-
